    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 requirements for a Class II device with medium model influence. Validation results VR-01, VR-02, and VR-04 demonstrate quantitative agreement with structured uncertainty quantification. Wall shear stress validation (VR-03) shows qualitative agreement with inherent variability assessed informally. Overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision that the CFD model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the CPB device.",
